                    <span>This is the best book on "helping" I have ever read. I use it constantly in my work as an organizational change consultant.<p>I highly recommend Edgar Schein's work to every manager and consultant I meet. Schein's work is amazingly insightful.<p>Buy this one today!<p>Dr. Michael Beitler<br>Author of "Strategic Organizational Change"</span>
                  
              
